{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Eversiege is a game where you have to find balance between your production and building defense to survive waves of enemies. Each siege defended provides experience that can be later spend on unlocking new buildings, leaders and upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PRODUCTION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Establish good economy by placing production buildings that'll give you various resources needed for further constructions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018990/extras/production.gif?t=1736166503\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DEFENSE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build defenses to protect your city from enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018990/extras/defense.gif?t=1736166503\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">REST</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you survive until the night, you will have some time to recover and prepare for further fights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018990/extras/night.gif?t=1736166503\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PLAN YOUR NEXT MOVE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When the siege ends, you'll need to decide which path to choose next. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018990/extras/map.gif?t=1736166503\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DEFEND, DEFEND, LOSE... REPEAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Even defeat won't stop you from trying again and again